text: Eddsworld is a British comedy/adventure web series created by Edd Gould. It premiered on June 6, 2003 and since then, it has been still airing with a crowdfunding campaign and has been published through Newgrounds, DeviantArt, YouTube, Albino Blacksheep, Tumblr, BBC, and their website. ==References== Category:Web series
title: Eddsworld
